name: Structure_Bocca_4-shelf_Narrow_Bookcase
description:
The Structure bookcase collection allows you to mix and match
pieces and add-in options to fit your space and your needs. This
four shelf bookcase is ideal when joining forces with other
Structure pieces to form a solid storage area or for use alone in a
space that needs structure. With adjustable shelves and a variety
of design combinations, the set up is compact and desirable for
multi-purpose living. Set includes: One (1) bookshelfMaterials: PEFC certified sustainable woodFinish: Oak, whiteDimensions: 59.5 inches high x 16.8 inches wide x 13.8 inches
